# SHIELD-PERSIST-LEAK (2026-04-21): PROPOSALS.md and TRUST_VIOLATIONS.md are
# working-artifact files that accumulate conversation state via the proposal-
# scraper hook and the API Death Shield auto-commit path. Conversation state
# can include NDA-protected topics, making these files a tracked-repo leak
# vector (verified by the 77fde23e near-miss on 2026-04-21). Files stay on
# disk for the Propose→Persist primitive and audit-trail uses; do NOT version-
# control their contents.
.claude/PROPOSALS.md
.claude/TRUST_VIOLATIONS.md

